"Always verify webhook signatures before processing payloads to ensure they "
"are authentic and haven't been tampered with."
msgstr ""
"Sempre verifique as assinaturas dos webhooks antes de processar as cargas "
"para garantir que sejam autênticas e não tenham sido manipuladas."

